# Normalize line endings to LF regardless of platform/core.autocrlf — a Windows
# checkout with autocrlf=true silently rewrites LF blobs to CRLF on checkout,
# which broke .claude/verify-harness.sh's hash comparison against a fresh
# Linux/CI checkout of the exact same commit (verify-harness.sh itself no
# longer reads the working tree for this reason, but every other tool that
# diffs/hashes file content benefits from this too).
* text=auto eol=lf
